26 Sec. 4. The Director of Administrative Services is hereby
27 authorized and directed to draw his or her warrants upon the funds in the
28 state treasury enumerated in this act, in favor of the several
29 beneficiaries named in this act for the amount set opposite their
30 respective names, upon the presentation of proper vouchers therefor. The
31 several amounts appropriated in this act shall be in full payment of any
-4-

LB1133 LB1133
2026 2026
1 and all claims, rights, causes of action, damages, and demands of every
2 character and kind owing by or against the State of Nebraska, its
3 officers, agents, and employees, and their successors and assigns with
4 respect to each of the beneficiaries respectively in whose favor the
5 appropriations are made. The director shall not deliver any warrant for
6 any items appropriated in this act until a receipt and release in full,
7 releasing the State of Nebraska, its officers, employees, and agents, and
8 their successors and assigns, has been filed by each of the beneficiaries
9 respectively. Upon presentation of the warrants, the State Treasurer is
10 hereby directed to pay the same out of money in the General Fund or out
11 of money in other funds indicated in this act not otherwise appropriated.
